  "2235200": {
    "name": "霓虹深渊2",
    "steam_appid": 2235200,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235200/extras/e46d6774b59818a3119bbffaccfe12ff.avif?t=1770089580\" width=780 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>为感谢各位早期玩家的支持，在《霓虹深渊2》抢先体验（EA）期间，所有已购买游戏本体的玩家均可直接免费领取该DLC。EA阶段结束后，您仍可永久保留该内容。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DLC内容：经过优化和升级，<strong>34个</strong>初代霓虹深渊BOSS将再次回归深渊！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >酷炫、梦幻、燃爆全场——经典动作Roguelike续作闪亮归来！深入《霓虹深渊2》美丽且危险的赛博神话世界，体验更快节奏的战斗、更严峻的考验、更多样的战斗风格以及意想不到的道具协同效果。享受肾上腺素飙升的瞬间，探索每一场令人难忘的冒险吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235200/extras/6421027d567cb5bf8a66441d6b3a37e2.avif?t=1770089580\" width=616 height=92 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235200/extras/ec2b0c4079ca5725a0aacac4f1835216.poster.avif?t=1770089580\" width=616 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235200/extras/ec2b0c4079ca5725a0aacac4f1835216.webm?t=1770089580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235200/extras/ec2b0c4079ca5725a0aacac4f1835216.mp4?t=1770089580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">《霓虹深渊2》最多支持4人联机游玩，准备叫上你的朋友一同开启这场全新的冒险吧！天知道你们会遇到些什么~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235200/extras/ef949c0912252c21983342623b23e6b3.avif?t=1770089580\" width=616 height=92 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235200/extras/8fe20b37379bbd8e7f9bf7a61e712fbe.poster.avif?t=1770089580\" width=616 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235200/extras/8fe20b37379bbd8e7f9bf7a61e712fbe.webm?t=1770089580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235200/extras/8fe20b37379bbd8e7f9bf7a61e712fbe.mp4?t=1770089580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">从挥舞球棒或光剑，到种植花朵攻击敌人，再到指挥神龙帮你作战——打开脑洞，尽情尝试各种奇思妙想的作战方式！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235200/extras/fab2e37a89cedcde503869f790ee1ee7.avif?t=1770089580\" width=616 height=92 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235200/extras/823c4e5b0d0557528a7b5f5e39c6c5e2.poster.avif?t=1770089580\" width=616 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235200/extras/823c4e5b0d0557528a7b5f5e39c6c5e2.webm?t=1770089580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235200/extras/823c4e5b0d0557528a7b5f5e39c6c5e2.mp4?t=1770089580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">获得道具赋予你千奇百怪的能力，这些能力还能相互联动，叠加数量更是没有限制。让敌人见识谁才是真正的 BOSS！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235200/extras/e042b17d823fcad1d50057a984c01e2c.avif?t=1770089580\" width=616 height=92 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235200/extras/4908224d5dae663f7e68b236d7c34929.poster.avif?t=1770089580\" width=616 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235200/extras/4908224d5dae663f7e68b236d7c34929.webm?t=1770089580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235200/extras/4908224d5dae663f7e68b236d7c34929.mp4?t=1770089580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">孵化并收集各种颜色的哈基宝（宠物），将它们组合进化成更强大的超级哈基宝。每只哈基宝都拥有独特的能力和机制，为游戏带来丰富多样的玩法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235200/extras/4078701a295d7df6efe98c99d122afd5.avif?t=1770089580\" width=616 height=92 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235200/extras/a06c94597607b8bfb5e7e9c4a10634f8.poster.avif?t=1770089580\" width=616 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235200/extras/a06c94597607b8bfb5e7e9c4a10634f8.webm?t=1770089580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235200/extras/a06c94597607b8bfb5e7e9c4a10634f8.mp4?t=1770089580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">全新的信仰系统赋予你运筹帷幄的能力。在宏伟的赌场中一决胜负，在琳琅满目的商店里尽情挥霍，或在萌宠乐园孵化可爱的哈基宝。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235200/extras/2e4a582fbd4c7f819b0f5dcf20605c1e.avif?t=1770089580\" width=616 height=92 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235200/extras/f4c9099cdf19a6f5fc036713dc2503a0.poster.avif?t=1770089580\" width=616 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235200/extras/f4c9099cdf19a6f5fc036713dc2503a0.webm?t=1770089580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235200/extras/f4c9099cdf19a6f5fc036713dc2503a0.mp4?t=1770089580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">神秘未知的邪恶力量，从未谋面的赛博新神，全面升级的宝物和战利品……还有更多全新系统和机制等待你挖掘。全副武装，同心协力，准备迎接新一轮的冒险吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
